      <title>Orientation</title>
      <section id="id1169867935002">
        <title>Textbook/Collection Layout</title>
        <para id="id1169865585984">The approach of this course will be to take the student through a progression of materials that will allow the student to develop the skills of programming. The basic unit of study is a Connexions module. Several modules are collected into a chapter. The chapters are divided into five groups. </para>
