</table><para id="eip-468">Some professors using this textbook/collection might decide to eliminate certain modules or chapters.  Some may eliminate the entire Advanced Topics group.  Other professors may choose to add additional study materials.  The advantage of this textbook/collection is that it may be adapted by professors to suit the needs of their students.</para>
